# vDSP_vqintD

**Function**

Calculates double-precision vector quadratic interpolation.

## Declaration

```swift
extern void vDSP_vqintD(const double * __A, const double * __B, vDSP_Stride __IB, double * __C, vDSP_Stride __IC, vDSP_Length __N, vDSP_Length __M);
```

## Discussion

This function is the same as [doc://com.apple.accelerate/documentation/Accelerate/vDSP_vqint], except for the types of vectors `A`, `B`, and `C`.

## Vector-to-Vector Quadratic Interpolation

- **vDSP_vqint**: Calculates single-precision vector quadratic interpolation.
